{{unreferenced|date=June 2010}}
'''Bizim Evin Halleri''' (Cases of Our House) is a long-running Turkish soap opera, which takes place in [[Ankara]], the capital of [[Turkey]].  It was first aired by [[Turkish Radio and Television Corporation|TRT]] in 2000.  From 2006 to 2008 it aired on  Kanal 1.  In Autumn of 2008 it transferred to [[ATV Turkey|Atv]].  However due to low ratings, Atv put an end to the soap opera.

